Developer documentation

The following pages are intended for WebGME users that intend to extend the basic WebGME framework with plugins or user-defined UI pieces.

  • Core - The most important API that holds the key for basic model manipulation and interpretation.
  • Client - The main entrypoint for UI extensions. This is the API that developers use for communication with the core on the client side in the UI.
